title: $1850/2BR  Heat Included

posting_body: ['Clean 2 bedroom apartment on the second floor in a 4 unit building.', ' Large eat in kitchen with many cabinets; also gas range and refrigerator.', ' Large porch off the kitchen.', ' Newly refinished oak hardwood floors in the bedrooms and living room.', ' Park like setting.', ' All apartments have been de-leaded.', 'Oil heat is included in the rental amount.', ' Tenant must pay for gas for cooking and hot water, electricity and cable.', ' Garage for one car and plenty of parking on site.', 'Located next to the Beechwood Knoll Elementary School.', 'Also included is a  storage locker in the basement.', ' There are coin operated washers and dryers on the property.', 'Please call 774-233-2220 and leave a message.', ' I will return your call as soon as possible.', ' Claire']
